"""
Onboarding ConversationHandler.

Three paths:
  C25K     (beginner):  Experience → Name → Location → done [3 steps]
  Full     (returning): Experience → Name → Mileage → VDOT method → Race dist
                         → Race date → Hilliness → Location → done [8 steps]
  Full     (regular):   Same as returning

VDOT method sub-paths:
  "I know it"        → enter number
  "Estimate from race" → pick distance → enter finish time → auto-calculate
  "Not sure"         → estimate from mileage silently, continue
"""
